name: Autumn Wind: Sherbet Edition
description:
Autumn Wind: Sherbet Edition is a reflective, calming meditation on movement. The work will begin in day or night mode, depending on your local time.

There are also interactive elements:
* Drag to the left, slow down, and reflect.
* Drag to the right, speed up, get lost in the emergent patterns.
* Double-click to change into day/night. If on mobile, shake your device.

Enjoy.
